# 5. Recommended First Algorithm (Graph Gravity)

## Step 1: Build kNN graph

## Step 2: Estimate density
ρ_i = average distance to neighbors

## Step 3: Assign mass
m_i = (ρ_i + ε)^γ

## Step 4: Define potential
Φ(i) = Σ_j m_j / (graph_distance(i,j)^α)

## Step 5: Flow rule
Each node moves to neighbor with highest Φ

Repeat until convergence.

## Step 6: Clusters
Nodes ending at same maximum = cluster

